05:24.525 --> 05:26.860
No, no, no, I don't need to know
the details, I don't need...

05:26.894 --> 05:28.896
All you need to know
is that the Staples Center,

05:28.929 --> 05:30.364
there's no way
they gonna pass on you.

05:30.398 --> 05:32.332
And regarding Michael,

05:32.366 --> 05:35.068
you got to put that
into the music, man.

05:36.537 --> 05:37.805
Come on.

05:37.838 --> 05:39.707
Engineer?

05:43.210 --> 05:45.613
(piano playing)

05:48.882 --> 05:52.753
