is probably worth 50 cents

06:39.633 --> 06:41.735
on Jamal Lyon's dollar.

06:55.916 --> 06:57.585
What, y'all some cowboys?

06:58.952 --> 07:01.655
What, y'all a bunch
of punk-ass cowboys?!

07:02.422 --> 07:04.625
Well, my name Hakeem...

07:04.658 --> 07:05.859
(groans)

07:07.795 --> 07:09.396
What was that, you little bitch?

07:09.429 --> 07:10.831
