07:19.172 --> 07:22.175
(Lucious sighs)

07:22.209 --> 07:24.244
Yeah, we gonna get
him back okay.

07:24.277 --> 07:26.580
How do you know?
How do you know, Lucious?

07:26.614 --> 07:29.483
Because they only
asked for $40,000.

07:29.517 --> 07:30.951
If this was
some long-term

07:30.984 --> 07:32.986
or they gonna hurt
him or kill him...

07:33.020 --> 07:34.855
Don't say that!
Don't say that!

07:34.888 --> 07:36.757
I'm just saying,
it's a simple snatch-and-grab.

07:36.790 --> 07:38.659
"Snatch-and-grab"?
Really, Lucious?

07:38.692 --> 07:40.594
You know where we come from,
ain't no such thing

07:40.628 --> 07:42.095
as no snatch-and-grab;
they snatch your ass,

07:42.129 --> 07:43.263
it's a wrap.

07:43.296 --> 07:44.364
Yeah, well,
things done changed.

07:44.397 --> 07:46.767
Nobody gets
bodied these days.

07:46.800 --> 07:48.135
You know, this is just

07:48.168 --> 07:50.604
somebody trying to
do a simple hustle

07:50.638 --> 07:51.639
and they flexing on you.

07:51.672 --> 07:53.507
Flexing on me?
Why me?!

07:53.541 --> 07:55.275
Because you're a
rookie to the block

07:55.308 --> 07:57.110
and they want
to remind you.

07:57.144 --> 07:59.880
