that you're my baby mama

07:59.913 --> 08:02.149
and they know that
he's related to me,

08:02.182 --> 08:03.784
so whatever happens,

08:03.817 --> 08:05.786
we're gonna get our
boy back, I swear.

08:05.819 --> 08:07.187
(cell phone ringing)

08:07.220 --> 08:09.557
Okay.
Go ahead.
That's them.

08:09.590 --> 08:11.825
Hello?

08:11.859 --> 08:14.361
Yep, we got the money.

08:14.394 --> 08:15.963
We at the drop-off!

08:15.996 --> 08:18.198
No, no, hold on,
hold on, hold on.

08:18.231 --> 08:19.867
Look, before we go any further,

08:19.900 --> 08:21.501
I want to know that
there's proof of life.

08:21.535 --> 08:23.671
Proof...?
Proof that he's okay.

08:23.704 --> 08:25.405
(whispers):
Proof of life?!

08:28.341 --> 08:30.477
Lucious and Cookie Lyon,
I'm still alive.

08:30.510 --> 08:33.881
This video is proof of life.

08:33.914 --> 08:36.149
I'm still here.

08:36.183 --> 08:38.018
Yeah, I see it.

08:38.051 --> 08:40.588
We're good, so...
where do you want it?

08:40.621 --> 08:42.322
Yeah, I see the
welding spot.

08:42.355 --> 08:43.323
All right.

08:43.356 --> 08:45.225
All right, thank you.

08:45.258 --> 08:46.359
What was that, Lucious?

08:46.393 --> 08:47.394
We're good to go.
Uh-huh.

08:47.427 --> 08:48.596
What was that?

08:48.629 --> 08:50.030
You said this was
just a snatch-and-grab.

08:50.063 --> 08:51.431
What is "proof of life"?

08:51.464 --> 08:53.601
Th-There's always
variables.

08:53.634 --> 08:55.402
Look, it's a different
time now, baby.

08:55.435 --> 08:57.204
Just stay calm.

08:57.237 --> 09:00.107
They said they gonna drop him
about three blocks west of here.

09:00.140 --> 09:02.542
This is the drop
spot for them.

09:02.576 --> 09:05.378
As we start rebranding Gutter
Life with me as president,

09:05.412 --> 09:07.080
