09:08.448 --> 09:10.250
the tickets sales,
digital downloads,

09:10.283 --> 09:12.953
tour grosses
and the algorithms.

09:12.986 --> 09:14.722
Mathematically, you can see
where our artists rank

09:14.755 --> 09:17.557
against other independent
labels of the same size.

09:17.591 --> 09:19.226
