what you learned

09:30.170 --> 09:31.639
from your Empire intern manual.
Not here for that.

09:31.672 --> 09:33.373
This all has to
mean something,

09:33.406 --> 09:34.808
ladies and gentlemen.

09:34.842 --> 09:36.644
Now, what if we based our roster

09:36.677 --> 09:38.578
on the wealth
of an individual's character,

09:38.612 --> 09:40.580
as well as their bottom line?

09:40.614 --> 09:43.150
Becky,

09:43.183 --> 09:45.218
can you set up a meeting for me
with each of these artists?

09:45.252 --> 09:48.789
